¶ Enchancia's queen ¶

08:46.960 --> 08:49.127
¶ It is clear to see ¶

08:49.129 --> 08:52.631
¶ That I was born
to rule ¶

08:52.633 --> 08:57.102
¶ Yes, it was meant to be ¶

08:58.672 --> 09:00.906
¶ I'm the one
who was supposed to ¶

09:00.908 --> 09:03.141
¶ End up on the throne ¶

09:03.143 --> 09:04.876
¶ Supposed to run this land ¶

09:04.878 --> 09:07.679
¶ And make the rules
all on my own ¶

09:07.681 --> 09:09.481
¶ If I show them all ¶

09:09.483 --> 09:12.918
¶ That Amber's
nothing but a fool ¶

09:12.920 --> 09:14.753
¶ They have got to see ¶

09:14.755 --> 09:19.491
¶ I'm far more fit to rule ¶

09:19.493 --> 09:21.760
-¶ I will be queen ¶
-¶ I will be king ¶

